Liau7 kun Sam-tiong7, ju7-mia5 To7-siu, Chiu7-si7 goa2 sou2-thiaN3 sou2 ng3-bang7 e5 hian5-iu2. “Gu2 un5 ti te7 bok8 jiok8 su,” ke2-soeh kong2, Chai hak8-seng e5 khoan2-sit, tok8-tok8 si7 sian-siN. Tui3 Beng5-ti7 30 ni5, Kau3-su7-hoe7 chhiaN2 goa2 jip8 Tiong-oh8 chou7-kau3, i chiu7 siok8 ti7 ji7-lian5-seng, hit-si5 chha-put-to 13 hoe3, chu-chit chhang-mia5, ia7 hun3-chi3 khin5-thak8, chin him-bou7 Han3-hak8, kiN3-na7 sou2 kho2 e5 long2 si7 saN-mia5-lai7.
Ti7 Tiong-oh8 thak8 kau3 chut-giap8, hit-si5 Hui3 Sian-siN u7 chhiaN2 i pang-chan7 ka3 chit8 ni5 ku2, au7-lai5 lip8-chi3 beh cho3 thoan5-kau3 e5 kang, chiu7 jip8 Sin5-hak8-hau7, si5-kan-lai7 khin5-khin5 kang2-kiu3 tak8 hang7 e5 hak8-bun7, si5-kan-goa7 chin jiat8-sim pou3-to7, chin ho2 khau2-chai5, thak8 kau3 chut-giap8 jian5-au7 koh khi3 Tang-kiaN jip8 Beng5-ti7-hak8-iN7 cho3 si3-lian5-seng chut-giap8 liau2 koh jip8 Cho2-tiu7-tian5 Tai7-hak8, kho2-sioh thak8 bo5 loa7-ku2 ku7-si5 e5 nau2-peN7 koh khi2, chiu7 tng2-lai5 Tai5-oan5 hioh-khun3. Kau3 chit pang koh khi3 Jit8-pun2 tiau7-iong2, bo5 phah-sng3 khi3 Tai7-pan2 e5 hai2-bin7 se2-ek8, kaN2-si7 bo5 lat8 thang siu5, chiah hou7 chui2 tu7--si2, kin-ni5 29 hoe3. 
Chiau3 lang5 teh kho2-lian5 i tui3 se3-han3 thak8-chheh kau3-taN, teh pi7-pan7 beh cho3 kau3-hoe7 e5 lou7-eng7, taN kap se3-kan soah, chiu7 i e5 chai5-tiau7 hak8-bun7 long2 toe3 chui2 lau5 khi3; kau3-hoe7 ia7 khiam3 chit8-e5 jin5-chai5, an2-ne khiok u7-iaN2, m7-ku2 Siong7-chu2 e5 chi2-i3 chin o3-biau7, hou7 lan2 be7-e7 chhek-tok8--tit. Kiam2-chhai2 Siong7-chu2 lin5-bin2 i e5 nau2-peN7, ai3 soah i e5 kan-khou2, sou2-i2 cha2-cha2 tiau3 i tng2-khi3 hou7 i hiong2-siu7 eng2-oan2 e5 khoaN3-oah8, an2-ne khiok iau2 khah ho2, tioh8 o-lo2 Siong7-chu2 e5 ho2 i3-su3. Cha2-cheng5 Khong2-chu2 u7 chit8 e5 hak8-seng seN3 Gan5 mia5 Hoe5; Khong2-chu2 o-lo2 i tek-heng7 chin ho2, kai3 thong-oh8 e5 gau5 thak8-chheh, u7 pang-chan7 ong5 e5 chai5-tiau7. Put-heng7 chiah8 kau3 32 hoe3 chiu7 koe3-sin, che ia7 si7 hou7 lang5 siuN7 be7 hiau2-tit. Liau7 kun Sam-tiong e5 cho-gu7 ia7 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ne.
