Phi2-jin5 u7 chih-tioh8 i e5 leng7-heng e5 phoe ai3 goa2 khi3 Sai-le5 hu3 chhe-ji7 sang3-chong3, goa2 chin ai3 the2-thiap, kho2-sioh iu5-pian7 chou2-tong3, kau3 chhe-ji7 me5 chiap-tioh8 phoe, sng3 si7 koe3-si5 lah, taN bo5 thang koh kiN3 i e5 bin7, tioh8 sia2 kui2-ku3 lai5 piau2 su-te7 e5 cheng5.
